Package: talatThaiR
Title: Access Thai Agricultural Statistics from NABC API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kanthanawit", "Jaisong", , "kanthanawit.jaisong@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a consistent interface to access Thai agricultural
    statistics from the National Agricultural Big Data Center (NABC) API.
    Supports daily, weekly, and monthly commodity prices as well as
    production and price indices at monthly, quarterly, and yearly
    frequencies. Features smart endpoint routing, built-in product code
    mappings, and automatic pagination.
